        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="s3_tasks" value="&amp;bull; Deploy Django API to Render (Gunicorn, env vars, auto-migrate)&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Deploy React SPA to Vercel (env var VITE_API_URL, SPA rewrites)&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Provision Supabase PostgreSQL + enable pgvector extension&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Configure OpenRouter API key + run document ingestion on Render&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; End-to-end user flow testing (login → train → compliance → incident → chat)&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; UI polish: responsive layout, loading states, error handling" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;fontColor=#334155;" vertex="1" parent="1">
